long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bring the universe to your Chrome new tab with a Digital Projection of a Planet live wallpaper, capturing the stunning beauty of outer space.

The Digital Projection of a Planet Live Wallpaper offers a mesmerizing display of a distant world, creating a captivating and futuristic new tab experience.

Features:
Digital Projection of a Planet Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension combines a cosmic chrome wallpaper with essential tools, making browsing both visually inspiring and functional. As one of the most unique chrome live wallpapers, it transforms your chrome background into a gateway to the stars.

For more live wallpapers, explore Gameograf.com. Check out extensions like: Galactic Nebula Live Wallpaper, Mars Terrain Live Wallpaper, Saturn Rings Live Wallpaper, Black Hole Live Wallpaper, Earth View Live Wallpaper.
